---
import '../styles/body.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <body>
        <!-- Header -->
        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="bg-neutral-800 bg-opacity-30 border-t-8 border-opacity-60 border-fuchsia-700 mt-24 py-32">
            <!-- Articles -->
            <main class="w-4/5 mx-auto flex flex-col items-center space-y-48">
                <!-- Leverage -->
                <article class="w-4/5 mx-auto flex xl:flex-row flex-col xl:items-start items-center justify-evenly xl:space-x-32 xl:space-y-0 space-y-24">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-start space-y-12 xl:pt-24" style="min-width: 400px">
                        <div class="pb-6 border-b-2 border-b-neutral-400 border-opacity-5">
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-3xl">Leverage To The <span class="text-fuchsia-500">Extreme</span></h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-5 w-11/12">
                                Crypto is all about freedom, so why should you be restricted when margin trading?
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-5 w-11/12">
                                While we advise against taking such risky positions, our protocol will let you
                                <span class="text-neutral-300">leverage up to a maximum of roughly 82x</span>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <a class="text-2xl px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-fuchsia-700 hover:bg-fuchsia-600 text-white font-bold glow" href="https://app.torque.money/"
                            >Leverage Now</a
                        >
                    </div>
                    <img class="glow rounded-xl" src="/assets/GRAPH.png" width="600" />
                </article>
                <!-- Provide -->
                <article class="w-4/5 mx-auto flex xl:flex-row flex-col xl:items-start items-center justify-evenly xl:space-x-32 xl:space-y-0 space-y-24">
                    <img src="/assets/TOKEN.png" width="400" style="filter: drop-shadow(-4px 8px 12px #842191)" />
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-end space-y-12 xl:pt-24" style="min-width: 400px">
                        <div class="text-right pb-6 border-b-2 border-b-neutral-400 border-opacity-5">
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-3xl">High <span class="text-fuchsia-500">APY</span> and Yields</h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-5 w-11/12 ml-auto">
                                Looking for <span class="text-neutral-300">high returns</span> without taking on the risks of leveraged trading?
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-5 w-11/12 ml-auto">
                                <span class="text-neutral-300">Provide liquidity</span> to our leveraging pool and you'll be rewarded with a
                                <span class="text-neutral-300">competitive APY</span>, while enjoying bonus yield farming rewards.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <a class="text-2xl px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-fuchsia-700 hover:bg-fuchsia-600 text-white font-bold glow" href="https://app.torque.money/"
                            >Add Liquidity</a
                        >
                    </div>
                </article>
                <!-- Trustless -->
                <article class="w-4/5 mx-auto flex xl:flex-row flex-col xl:items-start items-center justify-evenly xl:space-x-32 xl:space-y-0 space-y-24">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-start space-y-12 xl:pt-24" style="min-width: 400px">
                        <div class="pb-6 border-b-2 border-b-neutral-400 border-opacity-5">
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-3xl">Trustless. <span class="text-fuchsia-500">Permissionless</span>. Decentralized.</h3>
                            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-5 w-11/12">
                                100% of our services are managed entirely by smart contracts on the blockchain which can be audited by anyone, creating a completely
                                <span class="text-neutral-300">trustless</span> and <span class="text-neutral-300">decentralized</span> platform.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 font-medium mt-5 w-11/12">
                                Our services are also 100% equal for every single user, allowing us to present a truly
                                <span class="text-neutral-300">permissionless</span> system.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <a class="text-2xl px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-fuchsia-700 hover:bg-fuchsia-600 text-white font-bold glow" href="https://docs.torque.money/"
                            >Read The Docs</a
                        >
                    </div>
                    <img src="/assets/LOCK.svg" width="400" style="filter: drop-shadow(4px 8px 12px rgba(132, 33, 145, 0.5))" />
                </article>
            </main>
        </div>
        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="w-4/5 mx-auto">
            <ul class="text-neutral-400 text-lg font-medium flex items-center justify-start space-x-10 pb-6 pt-10">
                <li>
                    <a href="https://linktr.ee/torque_money">Links</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://app.torque.money/">App</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>